What you need to know:  Ochieng’ was a pillar in the Simba wa Nairobi midfield with his superb show convincing coach Nicholas Muyoti to name him in the four matchdays’ squadThe former Upper Hill School skipper’s journey in the topflight league kicked off on November 20 in the season opener against Bidco United at Nyayo National StadiumOchieng joined Nairobi City Stars from third tier side Vapor Sports in the last transfer window as Muyoti was beefing up his squad after mass exodus of 14 players who found greener pastures